an Rights Accountability Act），制裁阻礙香港落實民主普選和破壞香港自治的官員和警隊。俞懷松轉載有關帖文，並提議將葉劉列入制裁名單，更形容她是「好人選」。（She seems to be a good candidate for the Magnitsky list.）<br />\n<br />\n葉劉當時向傳媒反駁，自稱從來沒有侵犯人權或腐敗，又指該法案在2012年通過後，主要用來制裁侵犯人權的俄羅斯官員，「唔知關香港乜事」，亦非用來制裁民選議員。她直斥俞的言論完全荒謬、胡說八道和不知所謂，「唔知佢（俞）識唔識法律」，更質疑俞的身份，「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都唔知共和黨係咪真係有呢個人</span></span>」。"},{"pid":"ff7146a82b70855a546b0b0cca11c598133af00d","tid":1765451,"uid":158457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:21:52.000Z","msg":"好朋友先有好待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce1385a90a2dbde2eb26c50ef945a9030643c8e","tid":1765451,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdec77b1869ce2cce3d2211483fec23b8d562a2","tid":1765451,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1qtoKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1qtoKh.jpg&h=f1dcbf43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec7460614051d66ffd89ec3263046b2c1fa2c9ba","tid":1765451,"uid":278886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"希望你生生世世活係大灣區既壯麗山河之下"}]}